{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":false,"promptId":"839e3950-2d35-43f6-8d21-51ed0e1c39cc","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"what does 422 Unprocessable Content mean?"},"uuid":"5db789f2-cffe-4697-be20-192f4a3861fa","timestamp":"2026-04-20T16:34:11.295Z","permissionMode":"default","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/opt/development/git/shokworks/intellxxdna/terraform/intell-terraform-infra-azure","sessionId":"a0652cdb-de95-4368-b4b7-80d884950bec","version":"2.1.85","gitBranch":"main"}
{"parentUuid":"5db789f2-cffe-4697-be20-192f4a3861fa","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016cvfWrBkS8vjyioPiVmteb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**422 Unprocessable Content** (HTTP status code) means the server understood the request and the syntax is correct, but it couldn't process the contained instructions due to semantic errors.\n\nKey points:\n\n- The request is **well-formed** (valid JSON/XML syntax, correct Content-Type)\n- But the **data itself is invalid** — fails business logic or validation rules\n- Common causes:\n  - Missing required fields\n  - Invalid field values (e.g., wrong format, out-of-range numbers)\n  - Constraint violations (e.g., referencing a non-existent resource)\n  - Type mismatches\n\n**Difference from similar codes:**\n| Code | Meaning |\n|------|---------|\n| `400` | Malformed request (can't even parse it) |\n| `422` | Parseable but semantically invalid |\n| `404` | Resource not found |\n\n**Example:** Sending `{\"age\": \"not-a-number\"}` to an API expecting an integer — the JSON is valid, but the value fails validation → 422."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4546,"cache_read_input_tokens":11299,"output_tokens":246,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4546,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaFM3828hoYR745YWTpPn","type":"assistant","uuid":"c22a4d4e-5346-4c0f-886e-b24cd5536f2a","timestamp":"2026-04-20T16:34:17.114Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/opt/development/git/shokworks/intellxxdna/terraform/intell-terraform-infra-azure","sessionId":"a0652cdb-de95-4368-b4b7-80d884950bec","version":"2.1.85","gitBranch":"main"}
