{"parentUuid":"252ceabd-9baf-408a-80d1-7e4f1efbb198","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GR6wJLyPE8d7kRaZCTKmqV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Classic issue. The most likely cause is the browser is **not sending `Content-Type: application/json`**, so the server receives the body but can't parse it as JSON → 422.\n\n**Check your browser request code.** You probably have something like:\n\n```js\n// Missing Content-Type header - WRONG\nfetch('/rd/user/.../change-password', {\n  method: 'POST',\n  body: JSON.stringify({ new_password: '12345' })\n})\n```\n\n**Fix — add the header:**\n\n```js\nfetch('/rd/user/.../change-password', {\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: {\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json',  // <-- this is required\n  },\n  body: JSON.stringify({ new_password: '12345' })\n})\n```\n\nPostman sets `Content-Type: application/json` automatically when you select \"raw JSON\", but browsers don't add it unless you explicitly include it.\n\n**To confirm:** Open DevTools → Network tab → click the failing request → check the **Request Headers** — is `Content-Type: application/json` there?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":216,"cache_read_input_tokens":16346,"output_tokens":717,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":216,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CaFMQYLCmruWgB4nVH83K","type":"assistant","uuid":"8777fea0-232c-40e5-9431-d64740a9597e","timestamp":"2026-04-20T16:39:15.133Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/opt/development/git/shokworks/intellxxdna/terraform/intell-terraform-infra-azure","sessionId":"a0652cdb-de95-4368-b4b7-80d884950bec","version":"2.1.85","gitBranch":"main","slug":"shiny-cuddling-snail"}
